query:
INSERT INTO
                recursion_tip_witness_jobs_fri (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    recursion_tip_input_blob_url,
                    protocol_version,
                    status,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
                VALUES
                    ($1, $2, $3, 'waiting_for_proofs', NOW(), NOW())
                ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
                UPDATE
                SET
                    updated_at = NOW()
